| Role | Email | Password |
|------|-------|----------|
| Admin | admin@gmail.com | Admin123 |
| Founder | founder@demo.com | Demo123 |
| Specialist | specialist@demo.com | Demo123 |

---

## 🤖 AI Assistant Setup

The AI assistant uses Claude. To enable it:

```bash
# Set your Anthropic API key as an environment variable
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
```

Or on Windows:
```
set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
```

Without an API key, the AI assistant will show a friendly message explaining how to configure it. All other platform features work without it.

