## 📁 Project Structure

```
equiswap/
├── app.py                  # Main Flask application (all routes)
├── seed_data.py            # Demo data seeder
├── equiswap.db             # SQLite database (auto-created)
├── requirements.txt        # Python dependencies
├── templates/
│   ├── base.html           # Shared layout, sidebar, AI widget CSS
│   ├── index.html          # Landing page with real stats
│   ├── login.html          # Authentication
│   ├── signup.html         # Registration with role selection
│   ├── messages.html       # Real-time messaging page
│   └── dashboards/
│       ├── admin.html      # Analytics + user/post/app management
│       ├── founder.html    # Post management, applications, messaging
│       └── specialist.html # Browse posts, apply, track status
└── uploads/                # User uploaded files
    ├── avatars/
    ├── cvs/
    └── posts/
```

---

## ✨ Features

### Platform
- **Real stats** on landing page pulled from live database
- **Authentication** with hashed passwords (SHA-256)
- **Role-based access** — Admin, Founder, Specialist
- **File uploads** — profile photos, CVs, post attachments

### Admin Dashboard
- Live analytics charts (Chart.js) with real data
- User management (view, delete)
- Post management with application counts
- Application overview

### Founder Dashboard
- Create/manage posts with skills, deadlines, attachments
- Review applications — accept or reject
- Real-time style messaging with specialists
- **AI assistant** with full context of your posts and applicants
  - Ask: *"Is Marcus a good fit for my React post?"*
  - Ask: *"How can I improve my post to attract better applicants?"*

### Specialist Dashboard
- Browse all open posts with search/filter
- Apply with personalized message and highlighted skills
- Track application status
- **AI assistant** with full context
  - Ask: *"Is this founder worth working with?"*
  - Ask: *"How do I write a better application message?"*

### AI Assistant
- Knows your real account data (posts, applications, connections)
- Knows all live platform statistics
- Helps evaluate fit, improve applications/posts, strategic advice
- Chat history persisted per user in database
- Powered by Claude claude-sonnet-4-5

### Messaging
- Full conversation pages at `/messages/<partner_id>`
- Auto-polling every 3 seconds for new messages
- Unread message indicators
- AI assistant available on every conversation page

---

## 🗄️ Database Schema

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| users | All accounts (admin, founder, specialist) |
| posts | Founder service requests |
| applications | Specialist applications to posts |
| messages | Direct messages between users |
| ai_chats | AI conversation history per user |

---

## 🎨 Design

- **Colors:** Sage Green, Deep Teal, Soft Cloud White, Light Mist Gray
- **Fonts:** Cormorant Garamond (display) + DM Sans (body)
- **3D animation:** Three.js wireframe shapes on landing page
- **Charts:** Chart.js with real database data
- **Mobile responsive**

---

## 📦 Dependencies

Only one dependency needed:
```
flask>=3.0.0
```

Everything else uses Python stdlib:
- `sqlite3` — database
- `hashlib` — password hashing
- `json` — serialization
- `urllib` — AI API calls
- `secrets` — secure tokens
